<br>
The original spot was the signpost that was at the QH end of WK. However, since it was possible to very easily get yourself bugged in zone geometry and automatically moved to this location, they moved the spot to a few feet away from the NK zone line a long long time ago. If you port to WK and then Abscond, you will actually end up even further east than the wiz port puts you. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380>Qaman</a><BR>
